{"tid":1113492,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"父母自覺兒住公屋 求偶有優勢","createTime":"2019-04-18T02:37:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-20T13:21:17.000Z","uid":42188,"like":9,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":37,"replies":[{"pid":"ce7bf3bc7aa3233ebf4eaa444fd35ad6a0368c34","tid":1113492,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:37:45.000Z","msg":"樓價處於巔峰，部分人覺得有公屋住，總好過捱貴租。有網民指家長自覺住公屋的兒子是一個筍盤，婚後可跟父母同住，兒媳不愁無地方住。<br />\n<br />\n近日有網民在討論區發帖文，指有25歲獨生子，跟父母住公屋，副學士畢業的入他，月入約1.6萬元。家長有感兒子算孝順，每月薪水會交母親管理，又認為兒子是「筍盤」，形容「將來一家住公屋，兒媳返工賺錢養家，不愁住」。但網民卻不認同，揶揄其兒子收入不高、只住公屋，指他似「凶宅」多於「筍盤」。部分人認為，若果男生只想在公屋度過餘生，絕對不是筍盤，又譏笑「全家都窮，點可能係筍盤」。"},{"pid":"707fec1f0faf05396daf67759597c2bb20799e93","tid":1113492,"uid":20241,"like":44,"dislike":2,"score":42,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:40:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MynyxuX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMynyxuX.png&h=7e6435e5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"80469aeeb5801eff41b4754ebbf69bf9a9a43ce4","tid":1113492,"uid":9193,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:43:33.000Z","msg":"ON9"},{"pid":"90603d5d65e36df875a2fc9259863d9c4c7c74f2","tid":1113492,"uid":9193,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"冇樓幾靚仔幾考順都無用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d744f479d537ac25d55a3e40c9abbd4890b837be","tid":1113492,"uid":77092,"like":47,"dislike":1,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:44:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"365a0fa77352b0ebbc4391178fd341f373948db6","tid":1113492,"uid":19552,"like":10,"dislike":28,"score":-18,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T02:47:06.000Z","msg":"根本係香港住公屋有錢過住私樓<br />\n我識人幾百億身家都住公屋 因為實用D"},{"pid":"9b7c42d832911fcc090cf3be40b55e1dd0afe0fa","tid":1113492,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-18T03:30:42.000Z","msg":"公屋專員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":